## Contact API — email & SMS notifications (set the same variables in Vercel)

# Resend — https://resend.com
RESEND_API_KEY="re_XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX"
# Verified sender in Resend (e.g. "Fraaza Enterprises <notifications@yourdomain.com>")
RESEND_FROM_EMAIL="Fraaza Enterprises <notifications@yourdomain.com>"
# Owner inbox for new leads (comma-separated for multiple recipients)
NOTIFICATION_EMAIL="owner@example.com"

# Telnyx — https://telnyx.com
TELNYX_API_KEY="KEYXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX"
TELNYX_FROM_NUMBER="+1616XXXXXXX"
TELNYX_TO_NUMBER="+1616XXXXXXX"
# Optional — required for some number-pool / alphanumeric setups
# TELNYX_MESSAGING_PROFILE_ID="xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx"

## Marketing
GOOGLE_REVIEW_URL="https://www.google.com/search?q=Fraaza+Enterprises+Inc+Reviews#lrd=0x881990e04401c901:0x694e8308491078e7,3,,,,,"
